"nnoremap tn :tabnew<CR>

" Better window navigation
nnoremap <C-h> <C-w>h
nnoremap <C-j> <C-w>j
nnoremap <C-k> <C-w>k
nnoremap <C-l> <C-w>l

nnoremap <Leader>o o<Esc>^Da
nnoremap <Leader>O O<Esc>^Da
